        "description": {
          "value": "<p>This curse affects anyone who wears Knurlott's armor for at least 1 hour.</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:will|dc:37] save</p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 1 hour</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Doomed]{Doomed 1} and cannot remove the armor (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Doomed]{Doomed 2}, -10-foot status penalty to movement speeds, and cannot remove the armor (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> death, and transforms into Knurlott.</p>"
        },
